  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Kiln Ice', 'KI-68', 'Honey Crystal', null, 'KI-68 Honey Crystal is a warm, golden, and buttery yellow color The Kiln Ice glazes are modeled after traditional Guan or Snowflake glazes. They feature a delicate network of fine hairline cracks (known as “crazing”). Kiln Ice glazes are translucent, but become slightly opaque where the cracks form, creating a beautiful, multi-layered visual texture. Differences in glaze application and firing technique may affect end results These glazes are food safe, but due to durability, they are not recommended for food surfaces.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2353/3966/KI-68_1280pxX1280px_Website__94634.1741107589.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-1', 'Black', 'Cone 05', 'Black Liquid Underglaze is a deep obsidian black that is dark and smooth at cone 05, fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and maintains a deep black tone with a soft sheen all the way to cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Black an impeccably smooth finish with relatively good color, though it can cause small moments of transparency in the surface.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/761/1658/41141N__64806.1659287421.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-10', 'White', 'Cone 05', 'White Liquid Underglaze is a snow white that is light and dry at cone 05, a beautiful, slightly-warm white that fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and a slightly brighter white with a soft sheen at cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give White an impeccably smooth surface with good color.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/762/1657/41142P__06034.1659287325.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-15', 'Warm Gray', 'Cone 05', 'Warm Gray Liquid Underglaze is a soft gray that is light and smoky at cone 05, becomes deeper gray and fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and maintains a slate gray tone with a soft sheen all the way to cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Warm Gray an impeccably smooth surface with good color For Warm Gray Liquid Underglaze, we recommend using HF-9 Zinc Free Clear. If HF-10 Clear is used, color may shift HF-9 Zinc-Free Clear is recommended for use with underglazes to reduce the incidence of color shift. Most underglazes, stains, and coloring oxides will show their best color with Zinc-Free Clear.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/767/1613/41143B__67297.1659285784.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-20', 'Light Blue', 'Cone 05', 'Light Blue Liquid Underglaze is a pastel blue that is dry and soft at cone 05, becomes deeper in color and fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and maintains a sky blue tone with a soft sheen all the way to cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Light Blue an impeccably smooth surface with good color.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/768/1612/41144R__75125.1659285587.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-21', 'Medium Blue', 'Cone 05', 'Medium Blue Liquid Underglaze is an electric blue color that is soft and bright at cone 05, becomes more intense and fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and maintains a strong blue tone with a soft sheen all the way to cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Medium Blue an impeccably smooth finish with good color at cone 05 and cone 6, but tends to cause some transparency in the surface at cone 10.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/771/1578/41145B__15674.1659284218.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-22', 'Dark Blue', 'Cone 05', 'Dark Blue Liquid Underglaze is a deep navy that is a dark cobalt at cone 05, becomes a soft midnight blue and fluxes into a glaze-like surface at cone 6, and becomes almost black with a soft sheen at cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Dark Blue an impeccably smooth surface and intensify its color.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/772/1576/41146T__45635.1659284124.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-25', 'Turquoise', 'Cone 05', 'Turquoise Liquid Underglaze is a light teal color that is pastel and light at cone 05, becomes deeper teal and fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and maintains a blue green tone with a soft sheen at cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Turquoise an impeccably smooth surface with good color.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/773/1574/41147E__73204.1659283962.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-26', 'Aqua', 'Cone 05', 'Aqua Liquid Underglaze is a soft blue green that is very pastel at cone 05, becomes a much deeper blue green while fluxing into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and ends up losing a lot of color at cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Aqua an impeccably smooth surface with good color at cone 05 and cone 6, but can burn out some of the color at cone 10.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/774/1572/41148H__06797.1659283770.jpg?c=1'),
