  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Liquid Underglaze', 'LUG-50', 'Pink', 'Cone 05', 'Pink Liquid Underglaze is a cherry blossom pink that is a light blush color at cone 05, becomes warmer pink and fluxes into a soft glaze-like surface at cone 6, and is a warm salmon pink with a soft sheen at cone 10. Though the underglaze does become glaze-like, a clear gloss glaze can give Pink an impeccably smooth surface with good color.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/781/1557/41155D__92886.1659282552.jpg?c=1'),
