  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Low Fire Gloss', 'LG-68', 'Vivid Orange', 'Cone 05', 'Vivid Orange is a brilliant, glossy, semi- transparent cheddar orange glaze that breaks clear over textured surfaces.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/612/2390/LG-68_2x2_Fish_Tile__65202.1659448281.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Low Fire Gloss', 'LG-760', 'Pale Yellow', 'Cone 05', 'Pale Yellow is a brilliant, glossy, semi- transparent flaxen yellow glaze that breaks clear over textured surfaces.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/613/2387/LG-760_2x2_Fish_Tile__02130.1659448182.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Low Fire Matte', 'LM-10', 'Transparent Matte', 'Cone 05', 'Transparent Matte is a satin glaze that works well with surface decoration. If you spend all that time painting with Velvet Underglaze, make sure you use this to reduce the glare of a glossy glaze. Works great with any AMACO underglaze product. Apply thin over texture and surface decorations to prevent pooling. This glaze can become semi-opaque when it is thick.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2107/3290/lm10-transparent-matt-cup-rothshank-2048px__32587.1708031645.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Low Fire Matte', 'LM-11', 'Opaque White', 'Cone 05', 'Opaque White is a soft, matte bright white glaze that offers a unique, satin surface and will not flow during firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/616/2380/lm11-opaque-white-cup-rothshank-2048px__14878.1659447676.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-02', 'Black Tulip', 'Cone 05', 'Black Tulip is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a greenish obsidian where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/644/2300/o2-black-tulip-chip-2048px__07707.1659410331.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-10', 'Transparent Pearl', 'Cone 05', 'Transparent Pearl is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, milky white where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/641/2313/o10-transparent-pearl-chip-2048px__75292.1659410926.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-11', 'White Clover', 'Cone 05', 'White Clover is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a lovely light white where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/642/2309/o11-white-clover-chip-hires__50838.1659410708.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-12', 'Tawny', 'Cone 05', 'Tawny is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, sandy yellow where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/643/2307/o12-tawny-chip-2048px__83167.1659410583.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-20', 'Bluebell', 'Cone 05', 'Bluebell is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, powdery blue where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/645/2294/o20-bluebell-chip-2048px__92546.1659410064.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-21', 'Aquamarine', 'Cone 05', 'Aquamarine is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a rich, saturated teal where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/646/2292/o21-aquamarine-chip-2048px__27303.1659409787.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-23', 'Sapphire Blue', 'Cone 05', 'Sapphire Blue is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a rich electric blue where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/647/2287/o23-sapphire-blue-chip-2048px__84401.1659409493.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-26', 'Turquoise', 'Cone 05', 'Turquoise is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft cerulean where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/648/2282/o26-turquoise-chip-2048px__83997.1659409356.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-30', 'Autumn Leaf', 'Cone 05', 'Autumn Leaf is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, pale yellow where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/649/2277/o30-autumn-leaf-chip-2048px__46132.1659409125.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-42', 'Moss Green', 'Cone 05', 'Moss Green is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, mint green where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/650/2271/o42-moss-green-chip-2048px__00186.1659408951.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-52', 'Fuchsia', 'Cone 05', 'Fuchsia is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a bright cherry-blossom pink where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/651/2266/o52-fuchsia-chip-2048px__44282.1659408684.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-54', 'Dusty Rose', 'Cone 05', 'Dusty Rose is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a soft, milky pink where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/652/2260/o54-dusty-rose-chip-2048px__17796.1659408513.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Opalescent', 'O-57', 'Mottled Burgundy', 'Cone 05', 'Mottled Burgundy is an active, flowing low-fire glaze that breaks clear over texture and pools a rich, deep aubergine where thick. Because of its tendency to break and expose the clay body beneath, this glaze looks stunning over 67-M (Sedona) and over textured ware that has been painted with underglaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/653/2258/o57-mottled-burgundy-chip-2048px__75473.1659408375.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Phase Glaze', 'PG-24', 'Night Rain', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A deep indigo blue with lighter blue visual texture, PG-24 Night Rain is reminiscent of a night sky through a rain spattered window Layers well over AMACO Celadons, Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. For layering, please.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2310/3718/PG-24_NightRain_Cone5_WEB__86112.1710436832.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Phase Glaze', 'PG-42', 'Teal Drift', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A vivid turquoise with a subtle spots where thick, PG-42 Teal Drift is a rich, tropical color.Layers well over AMACO Celadons, Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. For layering, please.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2307/3706/PG-42_TealDrift_Cone5_WEB__80335.1710435840.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Phase Glaze', 'PG-54', 'Lunar Pink', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A pale, cool pink with white visual texture where thick. PG-54 Lunar Pink gives the visual effect of sunlight scattering through the Earth''s atmosphere during the moonrise.Layers well over AMACO Celadons, Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. For layering, please.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2308/3710/PG-54_LunarPink_Cone5_WEB__26378.1710435811.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Phase Glaze', 'PG-55', 'Floating Lavender', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A light purple with lighter visual spot texture where thick, PG-55 Floating Lavender is light and airy as a cloud at sunset. Layers well over AMACO Celadons, Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. For layering, please.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2309/3714/PG-55_FloatingLavendar_Cone5_WEB__04943.1710436139.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-01', 'Saturation Metallic', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Great for sculptural work and industrial ware, Saturation Metallic is a satin metallic black glaze that resembles steel and other metals. Saturation Metallic is great as an accent glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/458/2685/PC-1_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__86175.1659533154.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-02', 'Saturation Gold', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Saturation Gold has a smooth, satin/matte finish that is a dark gold similar to bronze when fired. Perfect for sculptural work and industrial ware, this glaze could be a unique accent for any work of art. Saturation Gold requires a heavy application to develop its gold metallic finish.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/460/2680/PC-2_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__96178.1659532908.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-04', 'Palladium', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This unique metallic glaze has a mirrorlike finish when fired and adds beautiful, shimmering accents to any work. Because it is not food safe, this glaze is perfect for sculptural work that calls for reflective, glassy surfaces. Palladium requires 3 coats to develop the smooth mirror finish. This glaze is fluid so be careful not to overfire. This glaze likes low porosity bodies. It is also great as an accent glaze or for layering with other AMACO glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/476/2646/PC-4_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__03947.1659465701.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-09', 'Vintage Gold', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Vintage Gold is a glossy metallic glaze which develops small triangular gold crystals with dark haloes like a glittering patina. This opaque glaze does not break over texture. For best results apply three even brush coats. ​A dramatic glaze for sculptural or non-functional work. Glaze may run.​.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2084/3260/PC-9VintageGold_GlazeChip_6x6__83854.1663164155.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-10', 'June Bug', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'June Bug is a glossy, dark green metallic glaze that develops small triangular iridescent crystals, like the wings of a beetle. This opaque glaze does not break over texture.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2295/3690/PC-10JuneBug_GlazeChip_6x6__42819.1708017434.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-11', 'Blue Spark', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Blue Spark is a glossy, royal blue glaze which develops small triangular dark gray metallic crystals that make this glaze look like lapis lazuli. This opaque glaze does not break over texture. For best results apply three even brush coats. Glaze may run.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2085/3261/PC-11BlueSpark_GlazeChip_6x6__99027.1663164367.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-12', 'Blue Midnight', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Blue Midnight is a glossy black glaze that breaks into blue highlights where thick. This glaze is good for textured work and also layers well with other Potter''s Choice Glazes. Blue Midnight benefits from a heavy application - it creates more separation from the base glaze to the float. Texture accentuates this effect.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/459/2684/PC-12_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__63317.1659533029.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-13', 'Serpentine Green', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This glaze is currently available at your local distributor PC-13 Serpentine Green is a semi-matte soft green glaze that breaks light blue over texture Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2366/4361/PC-13_Serpentine_Green_LabelTile_WEB__28641.1757687439.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-14', 'Lapis Flow', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This glaze is currently available at your local distributor Lapis Flow is a flowy glaze, varying in color from soft blue to purple and breaking green over texture Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2367/4362/PC-14_Lapis_Flow_LabelTile_WEB__65711.1757688104.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-15', 'Satin Oribe', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A modern take on a traditional Japanese oribe glaze, Satin Oribe adds a wonderful blue-green burnished look to your wares. Over texture, the dark green pools and light grey breaks bring an extra level of depth to this opaque glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2087/3265/PC-15_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip__57462.1663164980.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-16', 'Purple Crystal', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Purple Crystal is a matte violet glaze for Cone 5 that becomes glossy deep indigo with purple crystal floats at Cone 6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2088/3266/PC_PurpleCrystal_6x6Labeltile_WEB__54000.1663165185.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-17', 'Honey Flux', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Honey Flux is a creamy color that increases flow when layered over glazes. Opaque honey and cream at Cone 5 that shifts to a beautiful fluid white with honey flecks at Cone 6.​ Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2089/3267/PC_HoneyFlux_6x6Labeltile_WEB__81088.1663165449.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-18', 'Tuscan Blue', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This glaze is currently available at your local distributor PC-18 Tuscan Blue is a deep blue, semi-matte glaze that breaks light blue to moss green over texture Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2368/4363/PC-18_Tuscan_Blue_LabelTile_WEB__70856.1757688510.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-19', 'Moon River', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This glaze is currently available at your local distributor PC-19 Moon River is a dreamy, flowy glaze shifting in color from a soft periwinkle to a milky blue Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2369/4364/PC-19_Moon_River_LabelTile_WEB__39325.1757690055.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-20', 'Blue Rutile', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Great for layering and textured work, Blue Rutile is an active, complex glaze that is a flowing light blue where thick and breaks brown where thinner. Great for layering and always interesting, this glaze is always one of our top selling Potters Choice glazes! A very fluid glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/461/2678/PC-20_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__54961.1659532780.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-21', 'Arctic Blue', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Arctic Blue is a beautiful, opaque light blue that has a smooth, consistent surface and breaks tan over texture. This glaze lends very well to layering with other Potter''s Choice Glazes. Arctic Blue benefits from a heavy application.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/462/2676/PC-21_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__60400.1659532666.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-22', 'Blue Stone', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Similar in texture to a worn stone found at the bottom of a river, Blue Stone carries a softness that is visible in its smooth blue-green matte color. The different shades of green feather into dark blues when applied over texture wares.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2090/3268/PC-22_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip__14122.1663167729.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-23', 'Indigo Float', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Indigo Float is an intensely blue glaze with a lighter blue surface float. This rich cobalt glaze breaks deep blue where thinner. Great for layering with other potters choice glazes!', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/463/2673/PC-23_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__69644.1659532536.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-24', 'Sapphire Float', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Sapphire Float is a glossy, denim-blue glaze with a wispy white rutile float, that breaks a green-gray color over texture. The rutile float dramatically flows with texture and forms beautiful naturally flowing patterns.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2091/3269/PC-24_Sapphire_Float__80525.1663167957.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-25', 'Textured Turquoise', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'A subtle turquoise gloss, green-beige where thin, but a beautiful aqua where thick. Great for textured ware and layering with other Potter''s Choice glazes. It is a fluid glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/464/2671/PC-25_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__43675.1659532451.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-26', 'Blue Lagoon', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'The cool tones of Blue Lagoon break milky green and pool into light blue shallows when applied over deep texture. When heavier coats are applied this allows the glaze to float up and create interesting surface variations similar to tides in a blue lagoon. A fluid glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2092/3270/PC-26_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__00493.1663168137.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-27', 'Tourmaline', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Tourmaline is an intense, opaque blue-green glaze that forms a smooth, strong surface. Goes well layered with other potters choice glazes!', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/465/2669/PC-27_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__16243.1659532378.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-28', 'Frosted Turquoise', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Frosted Turquoise is an opaque gray-blue glaze that appears to crackle over deep blue but has a smooth, satiny surface. This glaze is a great, detailed surface decoration for subtle, simple forms. Frosted Turquoise benefits from a heavy application to achieve its color breaking effect. The glaze color is susceptible to variation due to iron fuming from nearby pots in firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/466/2667/PC-28_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__76599.1659532264.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-29', 'Deep Olive Speckle', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Deep Olive Speckle is a rich, translucent, glossy green glaze with darker green speckles. Looks great when layered with our other Potter''s Choice glazes. This glaze contains black speckles that may clog a spray gun. Make sure glaze is well-mixed for even distribution of speckles.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/467/2665/PC-29_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__45333.1659532134.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-30', 'Temmoku', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Temmoku is a textured, satin-matte dark brown/tan speckled glaze that looks great layered beneath some of the more fluid Potter''s Choice glazes. With its consistent surface and reliable results, this glaze makes a fantastic liner for cups, pots, bowls, and other ware.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/468/2664/PC-30_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__04587.1659532041.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-31', 'Oatmeal', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Oatmeal is a toasty, light beige glaze that is relatively translucent and breaks clear over textured surfaces. This glaze is great for layering with other Potters Choice glazes. Try layered over PC-33 Iron Lustre!', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/454/2694/PC-31_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__71374.1659533730.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-32', 'Albany Slip Brown', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Like the traditional potter''s glaze that inspired it, Albany Slip Brown is fluid and butter colored where thick and russet where thin. Great layered over or under other Potter''s Choice glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/469/2660/PC-32_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__89484.1659531904.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-33', 'Iron Lustre', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'More restrained, but similar to a regular blue glaze, Iron Lustre is brown where thin with blue-gray floats where thick. It is beautiful on texture and layers well with other Potter''s Choice glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/470/2658/PC-33_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__61306.1659531820.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-34', 'Light Sepia', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Light Sepia is an opalescent grey glaze that features strong variations on textured ware. This glaze breaks golden beige where thin and lends well to layering with our other Potters Choice Glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/471/2657/PC-34_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__84472.1659531661.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-36', 'Ironstone', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Ironstone is a glossy, dark glaze that is a deep chocolatey brown where thin with a beige-bronze float where thicker. Mixes well with other Potter''s Choice Glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/473/2651/PC-36_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__48479.1659531409.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-38', 'Iron Yellow', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Iron Yellow is a glossy, soft yellow glaze with flecks of iron, that is relatively opaque and breaks clear over texture. Excellent as a liner glaze for pots where the goal is to show off the decorations on the outside of the vessel.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2093/3271/PC-38_Iron_Yellow__39409.1663168567.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-40', 'True Celadon', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'True Celadon is a delicate light green glaze that reproduces the effects of traditional Asian celadons. This glaze looks striking over any textured ware and has great color response when layered with our other Potter''s Choice glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/477/2644/PC-40_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__79878.1659465592.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-41', 'Vert Lustre', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Vert Lustre is a beautiful flowing green glaze with a metallic sheen like that of ancient Persian Lusterware. This glaze reacts well to texture and has great effects when layered with other Potter''s Choice Glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/478/2642/PC-41_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__41955.1659465323.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-42', 'Seaweed', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Seaweed is a fluid, deep green glaze that layers beautifully with a variety of Potter''s Choice glazes. This glaze breaks brownish over texture and becomes more fluid with thickness. Pay attention to application thickness so the glaze does not flow onto kiln shelves during firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/479/2640/PC-42_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__74984.1659465238.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-43', 'Toasted Sage', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Toasted Sage is an opaque, warm gray glaze that has subtle, frothy tones of pink and green. This glaze layers very well with other Potter''s Choice glazes- particularly as a top coat.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/480/2638/PC-43_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__78039.1659465157.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-44', 'Sage', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Sage is an opaque, warm gray green glaze. This glaze layers very well with other Potter''s Choice glazes- particularly as a top coat.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2010/379/PC-44_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__54472.1658880561.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-45', 'Dark Green', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Dark green is a fluid, translucent emerald glaze that shows off textured and carved ware. Use over a wash of our High Fired Texturizer for added definition. Layers well with our other Potter''s Choice glazes!', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/455/2692/PC-45_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__54831.1659533630.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-46', 'Lustrous Jade', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Lustrous jade is a glossy, opaque glaze that boasts a soft, even green finish like the gemstone it is named for. This glaze layers well with our other Potter''s Choice glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/481/2635/PC-46_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__79867.1659465060.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-47', 'Emerald Falls', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Emerald Falls is a beautiful glossy green glaze that breaks lighter and pools into a mauve grey-green. When heavier coats are applied this allows the glaze to float up and create interesting surface variations echoing mossy patches found in rolling emerald landscapes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2094/3272/PC-47_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__26762.1663168805.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-48', 'Art Deco Green', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Art Deco Green is a glossy, light blue-green glaze that floats metallic spots to the surface resembling a patinate copper roof Clay body and application can affect the size and abundance of the metallic spots.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/482/2634/PC-48_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__30933.1659464921.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-49', 'Frosted Melon', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Frosted Melon is a very unique glaze with some qualities that can be exploited for additional interest. It has a massive, beige float with heavy application. This float "cracks", showing the green of the glaze below while still maintaining a smooth, satin surface. This subtle glaze is beautiful on smooth and textured ware alike.The glaze color is susceptible to variation due to iron fuming from other pots nearby in firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/483/2630/PC-49_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__57487.1659464753.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-52', 'Deep Sienna Speckle', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Deep Sienna Speckle is a warm, rich russet glaze that is translucent with dark speckles that resemble the surface of reduction stoneware glazes. For more depth and concentration of color, apply thicker. This glaze layers well with our other Potter''s Choice glazes. This glaze contains black speckles, so make sure glaze is mixed well to assure they are well dispersed. Specks may clog spray gun.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/485/2627/PC-52_6x6_Lablel_Tile_Chip-hires__56119.1659464566.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-53', 'Ancient Jasper', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Ancient Jasper is a fluid, opaque glaze that transitions from soft black to olive green to rust red as it is applied thicker. This glaze has an active, varied surface by itself and layers with our other Potter''s Choice glazes with striking results Ancient Jasper benefits from a heavier application. This glaze will produce reds on all clay bodies, although iron-bearing clay bodies will produce the widest range of colors. No special cooling cycles or soaks are needed. Soaking can actually diminish the reds.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/486/2626/PC-53_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__26696.1659464448.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-55', 'Chun Plum', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Chun Plum is a pink-red translucent glaze that breaks light tan over textures. This glaze imitates the copper reds of Asia but with a reliable color response in oxidation firings. Layer over other Potters Choice glazes for a warmer tone and hints of pink and red.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/487/2623/PC-55_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__83382.1659464356.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-56', 'Ancient Copper', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Inspired by classic tomato red reduction glazes, Ancient Copper is an iridescent, iron red glaze that breaks dark brown over texture and pools dark yellow-green, giving it a weathered appearance Ancient Copper is a satin at cone 5, and more glossy with metallic floats at cone 6. Avoid slow-cooling cycles when firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2326/3786/PC-56_Cone5_TileA_WEB__72288.1714744727.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-57', 'Smokey Merlot', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Smokey Merlot is a warm, dark purple glaze with a soft float of lilac over the surface. This glaze looks stunning on smooth surfaces, over textured surfaces, and layered with our other Potters Choice glazes.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/488/2622/PC-57_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__19436.1659464243.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-59', 'Deep Firebrick', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Deep Firebrick is an opaque, speckled brick red glaze that breaks translucent where thin. This bold, dark red glaze has a strong presence and layers well under or over other Potter''s Choice glazes. This glaze contains black specks that may clog spray guns. Make sure glaze is well-mixed to ensure even distribution of speckles.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/489/2618/large_pc59-application-tiles-and-sake-cup-2048px__43383.1708017541.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-61', 'Textured Amber', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Textured Amber is a semi-matte brown glaze that has a varied, translucent surface with a textured float of opaque tan speckles. Try layering this glaze with our other Potter''s Choice glazes!', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/456/2689/PC-61_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__01500.1659533466.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-62', 'Textured Amber Brown', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Textured Amber Brown is a glossy brown glaze that breaks lighter where thinner like a traditional temmoku glaze. This glaze layers well with our other Potter''s Choice glazes and produces fluid, beautiful effects.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/457/2688/PC-62_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip-hires__42212.1659533292.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-63', 'Cosmic Tea Dust', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Cosmic Tea Dust is a sparkly, dark brown glaze, which breaks a light yellow-brown over texture. The sparkle shifts subtly from silver to copper to give the glaze an iridescent quality.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2097/3275/PC-63_Cosmic_Tea_Dust__35816.1663169398.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-64', 'Aventurine', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Aventurine is an amber glaze with crystal flecks, that breaks golden over texture and pools a darker shade in recessed areas. This glaze is fluid so leave room for vertical flow. Testing is recommended to find the proper application and firing.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2098/3276/PC-64_Aventurine__46364.1663169684.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-65', 'Black Aventurine', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Black Aventurine is a fluid, rich black glaze that develops a metallic sparkle.​ If slow cooled, this glaze will grow crystals.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2099/3277/PC_BlackAventuring_6x6Labeltile_WEB__70396.1663169904.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-66', 'Cosmic Oilspot', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Cosmic Oil Spot is a dark glaze with shimmery flecks that create streams and spots of color similar to a traditional hare’s fur glaze.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2100/3278/PC_CosmicOilspot_6x6Labeltile_WEB__76300.1663170137.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-67', 'River Rock', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'The sandy, dark brown tones of River Rock feather into a beautiful ebony before breaking into a rich amber when applied over texture. Subtle green-grey honeycomb shapes appear underneath the amber breaks when this glossy glaze is applied on vertical surfaces.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2101/3279/PC-67_6x6_Label_Tile_Chip__16686.1663170316.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-68', 'Golden Honey', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Semi-gloss warm yellow, Golden Honey is a translucent glaze like whipped honey. Breaks lighter on texture, a richer color where thick Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2311/3744/PC-68_GoldenHoney_Cone5_WEB__87996.1711484588.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-69', 'Cosmic Gold Dust', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'This glaze is currently available at your local distributor PC-69 Cosmic Gold Dust is a sparkly gold glaze with subtle specks of reds and browns in the light Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes. Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2370/4365/PC-69_Cosmic_Gold_Dust_LabelTile_WEB__86129.1757690442.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-70', 'Copper Red', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Copper Red is an oxblood red that gives the same results in oxidation as a traditional reduction copper glaze​. Copper Red breaks clear on edges or where thin.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2102/3280/PC-70CopperRed_GlazeChip_6x6__28241.1663170559.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-71', 'Flambe', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Flambé​ is a copper red glaze with tones of purple and blue, that gives the same results in oxidation as a traditional reduction copper glaze. Flambé breaks clear on edges or where thin.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2103/3281/PC-71Flambe_GlazeChip_6x6__44221.1663170895.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice', 'PC-72', 'Fire & Ice', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PC-72 Fire & Ice is deep red where thick and icy blue where thin. Fire & Ice is a reduction copper red for electric firing with a dramatic icy blue-colored break on texture. Apply three coats for best oxblood red color Layers well over AMACO Celadons, other Potter''s Choice and Satin Matte glazes.Glaze layering fired results may run if paired with a runny glaze. We recommend testing any layering combination prior to putting it on a full ceramic piece Shake well before use.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2312/3746/PC-72_FireAndIce_Cone5_WEB__23034.1711485298.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-03', 'Midnight Run', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-3 Midnight Run is a glossy dark blue-gray glaze like a velvety night sky Breaks dark across textured surfaces. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay. Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2288/3670/PCF-3_Cone5_WebsiteSwatch__18349.1707272010.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-16', 'Aurora Breeze', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-16 Aurora Breeze is a hazy pink glaze with hints of blue and purple and dark speckles. It breaks across textured surfaces, developing a warm blush float when thick. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Shake well before use. Thin with water and AMACO® Gum Solution if needed. Apply 3 even coats of glaze to Cone 04 bisque. (Let the glaze dry between coats.) Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2337/3912/PCF-16_AuroraBreeze_SquareTile_WEB__16806.1733270912.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-18', 'Honeydew', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-18 Honeydew is a glossy pale green glaze like the melon it''s named for. It breaks across textured surfaces and develops a peachy float when thick. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat Beautiful on any color of clay. Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2289/3674/PCF-18_Cone5_WebsiteSwatch__19242.1707272515.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-19', 'Cirrus Flow', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-19 Cirrus Flow is a glossy pale blue glaze like a delicate cloud. This glaze breaks across textured surfaces and develops a peachy float when thick. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat Beautiful on any color of clay. Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2290/3678/PCF-19_Cone5_WebsiteSwatch__43685.1707272782.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-21', 'Ocean Drift', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-21 Ocean Drift is a calming blue color, interspersed with fine, dark speckles that add texture and visual interest. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Shake well before use. Thin with water and AMACO® Gum Solution if needed. Apply 3 even coats of glaze to Cone 04 bisque. (Let the glaze dry between coats.) Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2338/3914/PCF-21_OceanDrift_SquareTile_WEB__44427.1733271396.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-33', 'Mystic Tide', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-33 Mystic Tide is earthy green, highlighted by a subtle, mottled texture that adds depth and complexity to the surface. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Shake well before use. Thin with water and AMACO® Gum Solution if needed. Apply 3 even coats of glaze to Cone 04 bisque. (Let the glaze dry between coats.) Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2339/3917/PCF-33_MysticTide_SquareTile_WEB__28691.1733271879.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-36', 'Rose Mist', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-36 Rose Mist features a soft, blush-pink base, with subtle hints of lavender and white swirls. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Shake well before use. Thin with water and AMACO® Gum Solution if needed. Apply 3 even coats of glaze to Cone 04 bisque. (Let the glaze dry between coats.) Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2340/3920/PCF-36_Rosemist_SquareTile_WEB__22958.1733272409.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-54', 'Flux Blossom', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-54 Flux Blossom is glossy pale pink glaze like a fresh flower. It breaks across textured surfaces and develops a nice peachy float when thick. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat Beautiful on any color of clay. Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2291/3680/PCF-54_Cone5_WebsiteSwatch__83436.1707273072.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-60', 'Sunbeam', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-60 Sunbeam is a radiant golden-yellow with subtle gradations of amber and honey. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat. Beautiful on any color of clay Good at cone 5, more fluid at cone 6 Shake well before use. Thin with water and AMACO® Gum Solution if needed. Apply 3 even coats of glaze to Cone 04 bisque. (Let the glaze dry between coats.) Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2341/3921/PCF-60_Sunbeam_SquareTile_WEB__59277.1733272609.jpg?c=1'),
