  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Potter''s Choice Flux', 'PCF-74', 'River Birch', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'PCF-74 River Birch is a glossy cream glaze with runny dark specks like the bark of a tree. River Birch breaks across textured surfaces and develops a peachy float when thick. Great for layering with other glazes as a base or top coat Beautiful on any color of clay. Very fluid at cone 5, more so at cone 6 Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2292/3682/PCF-74_Cone5_WebsiteSwatch__29713.1707273216.jpg?c=1'),
