  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Satin Matte', 'SM-03', 'Marble', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'SM-3 Marble is a pale gray satin glaze, just a whisper of color like the polished marble it''s inspired by Glaze fire to Cone 5-6.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/2283/3868/ProductImages_SM-3__42115.1723138733.jpg?c=1'),
  ('commercial', 'AMACO', 'Satin Matte', 'SM-10', 'Clear Satin', 'Cone 5 / Cone 6', 'Clear Satin is a smooth, buttery zinc-free clear glaze that accentuates textured ware and boasts a classic art deco appearance. Add SM-10 to other Satin Matte colors to create softer tones. Use 2 coats over underglazes for a more translucent result. Zinc-free.Some underglaze colors may be muted with SM-10 Clear Satin: V-370 Velour Black V-361 Jet Black V-316 Light Pink.', 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-a0h9fhqogk/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/655/3864/ProductImages_SM-10__76260.1722962393.jpg?c=1'),
